ETHSF Hackathon Project
Alacris Ad Revenue Demo

1. Browser Extension
- Allows entry of public key
- Allows Public Key to be pulled from a website
- Allows Public Key to be deleted
- Displays Alacris On-Chain Balance

2. Host website
- Sends JS that embeds an iframe ad that pulls Public Key from the Browser and creates the URL with both Public Keys so the Ad Supplier can pay out

3. Ad Server
- Parses both Public Keys from URL 
- Makes a payment request to both Key
- Display Ad